    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0002",
      "text": " 99",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0003",
      "text": "ns.  Every other bit value is a binary multiple of this value.  The next most significant bit is 2x that val-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        539.95,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0004",
      "text": "ue, or 18,8ns.  The next least significant value is ½ that value, or 4.7ns.  The overall least significant",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        540.0,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0005",
      "text": "bit is 73,5ps.  The overall range that may be represented is 1,36 x 10",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        398.08,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0006",
      "text": "9",
      "bbox": [
        398.1,
        79.42,
        402.54,
        88.32
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0007",
      "text": " sec, approximately equal to 43",
      "bbox": [
        402.54,
        81.65,
        539.96,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0008",
      "text": "years.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        93.65,
        123.18,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0009",
      "text": "The Clock Count value shall represent the time at which the most significant bit was placed on the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        540.01,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0010",
      "text": "link by the CSU ELS originator.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        233.78,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0011",
      "text": "Any bits outside the range of CS_Implemented_MSB to CS_Implemented_LSB shall be set to zero.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.97,
        540.0,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0012",
      "text": "This applies to both the Clock Sync Server and to the Fabric.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.97,
        364.9,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0013",
      "text": "4.2.36.4  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.97,
        214.86,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0014",
      "text": "none.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        120.96,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0015",
      "text": "4.2.37",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        123.74,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0016",
      "text": "Report Port Buffer Conditions (RPBC)",
      "bbox": [
        133.8,
        238.96,
        313.62,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0017",
      "text": "4.2.37.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        192.63,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0018",
      "text": "The RPBC ELS shall provide a method for a Port to report its buffer conditions.  The normal response",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        539.98,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0019",
      "text": "to an RPBC ELS Sequence shall be a LS_ACC ELS Sequence.  If the recipient Port does not support",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        540.03,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0020",
      "text": "the RPBC ELS, it shall reply with an LS_RJT ELS Sequence with a reason code of \"Command not",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        540.07,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0021",
      "text": "supported\".  ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        152.28,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0022",
      "text": "4.2.37.2  Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        178.22,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0023",
      "text": "a) Report Port Buffer Conditions (RPBC) Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        370.96,
        377.86,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0024",
      "text": "b) LS_ACC or LS_RJT Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        394.96,
        287.89,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0025",
      "text": "4.2.37.3  Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        227.06,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0026",
      "text": "Addressing: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        157.1,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0027",
      "text": "The S_ID designates the source port that is requesting port buffer conditions.  The",
      "bbox": [
        157.08,
        442.96,
        539.89,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0028",
      "text": "D_ID field designates the recipient that is to process the RPBC request and report buffer conditions.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        536.92,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0029",
      "text": "Payload: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        140.41,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p118_s0030",
      "text": "The format of the RPBC Payload is shown in table 101.",
      "bbox": [
        140.4,
        478.96,
        384.85,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
